@NODE INTRODUCTION "Introduction"
This is yet another MineSweeper clone for Amiga. The reason why it's made
is simply because I wanted to do my own and try to make it atleast just a
little bit better than the other versions I've seen.

The reason of the strange name is because the swedish army has a
"minesweeper" called Glufs-Glufs. That's why! :-)

@ENDNODE

@NODE INSTALLATION "Installation"
Simply copy the GlufsMines directory where you want it, no assign's or
anything else needed. The game will create a highscore file in the
startup-path called Glufs.scores.

@ENDNODE

